<p>Expo&#x27;s GCP infrastructure is properly configured as high-availability to ensure proper failover in case of a zone failure. Daily encrypted backups are kept in GCP. While never expected, we are prepared to restore data from backups in the event of a production data loss. Expo performs regular technical and procedural testing of our disaster recovery plan.</p>
