<p>User data is immediately scheduled for timely deletion upon deletion of a user profile or account. To ensure they are authorized to do so, users must delete their accounts from within the Expo user interface. One a user profile or account is deleted, a job is initiated to delete any corresponding records stored by a <a class="text-link transition-opacity hocus:opacity-80" href="/privacy/subprocessors">subprocessor</a>.</p>
