<p>Vulnerabilities related to Expo tools can be reported to <a class="text-link transition-opacity hocus:opacity-80" href="mailto:vulnerability-disclosures@expo.dev">vulnerability-disclosures@expo.dev</a>. Be sure to include a proof of concept, a list of tools used (including versions), and the output of the tools. We take all disclosures seriously and will respond to valid reports as we verify the vulnerability and develop a fix.</p>
